title: Dot and the kangaroo Box Set 1977 NTSC
description:
This is the Dot and the kanagoo box set, I converted it from pal to ntsc. the video is a little low end by todays standards,
 but its from the late 70's and early 80's so its right on par for when i watched it on tv as a kid. I hope you enjoy it. 
Please seed as you can as i need the bandwith for work so can only seed when im not working.

all 512x384 res in avi format
